org.cloudbus.cloudsim

Class CloudletAbstract.ExecutionInDatacenterInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cloudbus.cloudsim.CloudletAbstract.ExecutionInDatacenterInfo
  • Enclosing class:
    CloudletAbstract

    protected static class CloudletAbstract.ExecutionInDatacenterInfo
extends Object
    Internal class that keeps track of Cloudlet's movement in different Datacenters. Each time a cloudlet is run on a given Datacenter, the cloudlet's execution history on each Datacenter is registered at CloudletAbstract.getExecutionInDatacenterInfoList()
